text: Gerry Mullins (born 29 December 1953) is an Irish equestrian. He competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Irish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Ireland Category:Equestrians at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
